    "text": [
        "Dear Mr Philips,",
        "I am writing this letter to invite you and your family to be at my inaugural party in the neighbourhood.",
        "Let me start by introducing myself. I am your new neighbour, from 25 Bridgeway Street, and I have been recently relocated from Montreal to here, in order to help my company in the development of the new office in town.",
        "As for my plans for the party, considering that I have just arrived and barely know the people around here, it would be a good start for me to get to know my new neighbours and new colleagues at work. So, the party will be very informal, with some beers and finger food.",
        "Thus, I would like to kindly ask if you and your family would be willing to come. The party will be next Friday, starting at 6pm. Please let me know if you have any allergies.",
        "I look forward to hearing a positive response from you.",
        "Yours sincerely,",
        "Christina"
